{"tid":2456500,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢只係當我係PTGF 仲要唔使錢","createTime":"2021-03-22T03:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T16:07:56.000Z","uid":4618,"like":17,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f076bda46a4a40584271805dfe0e37268b7fb65b","tid":2456500,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"咁啱有一次同佢飲大咗上左酒店<br />\n<br />\n之後佢對我幾好<br />\n呢2個月嚟成日都會出街<br />\n連情人節都有晏就出街<br />\n<br />\n但佢今日同我講佢追緊一個係交友app識既女仔<br />\n我個一刻呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話一直當我係好朋友<br />\n只係friend with benefit<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來我一直只係佢唔使比錢既PTGF<br />\n只係我沉左船<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c026862f56bf1f05d4720cf60d39949443d947","tid":2456500,"uid":30098,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"8b42b09415a4074d403bbe3623bcaf588925a367","tid":2456500,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"62c026862f56bf1f05d4720cf60d39949443d947","tid":2456500,"uid":30098,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"抵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"呢個世界要搵一段真感情係咪咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f485c9a08ce166a018f4a167737afad8c58aee90","tid":2456500,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"好似香討見過"},{"pid":"5ce5d4789dcc5cb5b1b52d098548d94721c5a50e","tid":2456500,"uid":51033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"人地做返直仔啫"},{"pid":"9ad4211e2cbcc685c12e7059f6a8d4a94b397f70","tid":2456500,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f485c9a08ce166a018f4a167737afad8c58aee90","tid":2456500,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:54:06.000Z","ms